data.description: This Super CUTE and So Very Charming Brick Bungalow will win your heart with its Window Seats, Gorgeous French Doors, Arches, and Sweet Nooks and Built ins. The Expansive Front Porch is like an extended seasonal living area. Inside, it's light and bright with lots of windows. So spacious with a large open concept living room with a gorgeous archway that opens to a roomy dining room and into a large kitchen with a pantry and cute breakfast nook. Hardwoods throughout. The spacious and flat backyard is a big plus. This bungalow has so much HGTV decoration potential to make this home your very own unique sanctuary. Full basement with laundry area. Two sheds on the property. Don't wait on this one! It's waiting for you to make it yours and it's priced well to sell!
